 "data": "@startuml
entity Users {
 +user_id: INT <<PK>>
 --
 username: VARCHAR(50) <<Unique>>
 email: VARCHAR(100) <<Unique>>
 password_hash: VARCHAR(255)
 full_name: VARCHAR(100)
 phone_number: VARCHAR(15)
 user_role: VARCHAR(20)
 created_at: TIMESTAMP
 updated_at: TIMESTAMP
}

entity Lodges {
 +lodge_id: INT <<PK>>
 --
 owner_id: INT <<FK>>
 lodge_name: VARCHAR(100)
 address: VARCHAR(255)
 city: VARCHAR(100)
 state: VARCHAR(100)
 country: VARCHAR(100)
 postal_code: VARCHAR(20)
 description: TEXT
 amenities: TEXT
 contact_number: VARCHAR(15)
 website_url: VARCHAR(255)
 created_at: TIMESTAMP
 updated_at: TIMESTAMP
}

entity Rooms {
 +room_id: INT <<PK>>
 --
 lodge_id: INT <<FK>>
 room_type: VARCHAR(50)
 room_number: VARCHAR(50)
 description: TEXT
 price_per_night: DECIMAL(10, 2)
 max_occupancy: INT
 is_available: BOOLEAN
 created_at: TIMESTAMP
 updated_at: TIMESTAMP
}

entity Bookings {
 +booking_id: INT <<PK>>
 --
 user_id: INT <<FK>>
 room_id: INT <<FK>>
 check_in_date: DATE
 check_out_date: DATE
 total_price: DECIMAL(10, 2)
 booking_status: VARCHAR(20)
 created_at: TIMESTAMP
 updated_at: TIMESTAMP
}

entity Payments {
 +payment_id: INT <<PK>>
 --
 booking_id: INT <<FK>>
 payment_date: TIMESTAMP
 amount: DECIMAL(10, 2)
 payment_method: VARCHAR(50)
 payment_status: VARCHAR(20)
 created_at: TIMESTAMP
 updated_at: TIMESTAMP
}

entity Reviews {
 +review_id: INT <<PK>>
 --
 user_id: INT <<FK>>
 lodge_id: INT <<FK>>
 rating: INT
 comment: TEXT
 created_at: TIMESTAMP
 updated_at: TIMESTAMP
}

entity Room_Availability {
 +availability_id: INT <<PK>>
 --
 room_id: INT <<FK>>
 date: DATE
 is_available: BOOLEAN
 created_at: TIMESTAMP
 updated_at: TIMESTAMP
}

entity Images {
 +image_id: INT <<PK>>
 --
 lodge_id: INT <<FK>>
 room_id: INT <<FK>>
 image_url: VARCHAR(255)
 uploaded_at: TIMESTAMP
}

entity Amenities {
 +amenity_id: INT <<PK>>
 --
 amenity_name: VARCHAR(100)
}

entity Lodge_Amenities {
 +lodge_id: INT <<FK>>
 +amenity_id: INT <<FK>>
 --
 <<PK>> lodge_id, amenity_id
}

entity Room_Amenities {
 +room_id: INT <<FK>>
 +amenity_id: INT <<FK>>
 --
 <<PK>> room_id, amenity_id
}

entity Notifications {
 +notification_id: INT <<PK>>
 --
 user_id: INT <<FK>>
 message: TEXT
 is_read: BOOLEAN
 created_at: TIMESTAMP
}

entity Support_Requests {
 +request_id: INT <<PK>>
 --
 user_id: INT <<FK>>
 subject: VARCHAR(255)
 message: TEXT
 status: VARCHAR(20)
 created_at: TIMESTAMP
 updated_at: TIMESTAMP
}

Users ||--o{ Lodges: \"manages\"
Lodges ||--o{ Rooms: \"contains\"
Rooms ||--o{ Bookings: \"has\"
Users ||--o{ Bookings: \"makes\"
Bookings ||--|| Payments: \"is paid by\"
Lodges ||--o{ Reviews: \"receives\"
Users ||--o{ Reviews: \"writes\"
Rooms ||--o{ Room_Availability: \"is available at\"
Lodges ||--o{ Images: \"has\"
Rooms ||--o{ Images: \"has\"
Lodges }o--o{ Lodge_Amenities: \"has\"
Rooms }o--o{ Room_Amenities: \"has\"
Users ||--o{ Notifications: \"receives\"
Users ||--o{ Support_Requests: \"submits\"
@enduml
